data.description: This single story home built by Calatlantic homes has a spacious open floor plan with Family Room that connects to a open Kitchen, large Breakfast Nook, and formal Dining Room, offering unparalleled connectivity. It features a craftsman's exterior elevation with a front porch and 3-car garage. It is in Keystone Ridge Estates, a private gated community in Pinellas County with only 35 home sites, at the north end of Lake Tarpon. This home is a must see!!  Home also features granite counter tops with 42 inch cabinets. wine and coffee stations as well as knock down textures, upgraded tile floors though-out with upgraded carpets in the bedrooms. upgrade bathrooms, Home has high ceilings through-out, with a great amount of closet space it gives you what a lot of homes do not. Exterior features include upgrade Zosia lawn, sprinkler system, upgrade landscaping, rock vs mulch for no more mess and easy care, paver driveway and walk. owner is offering it including new interior paint by professional painter, colors at buyers choice
